document_data.name: Five Fine Fish
document_data.mainbody: The '''Five Fine Fish''' was a [[tavern]] located in the town of [[Immersea]] in [[Cormyr]] during the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].{{Cite interactive atlas|4300 Immersea}}
document_data.Location: The tavern was located on the eastern side of Immersea near the shores of the [[Wyvernwater]]. It sat on the northwest corner of [[Calantar's Way]] opposite a statue of [[Azoun Obarskyr III]].
